	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[4.40]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>All SS quest items drop in Temple of Veeshan, Halls of Testing.&nbsp;&nbsp;This drop is rare (BP's, Legs, Robes are the rarest).<br><br>You must have minimum dubious to CoV to get through WW and into ToV without fighting.  There are no CoV faction hits for killing the mobs in HoT.<br><br>The gems for these quests drop in Cobalt Scar, Sirens Grotto, and Velks that I'm aware of.  Cobalt Scar is mostly flawed and chipped gems.  SG and Velks are where the crushed and pristine gems drop.<br><br>Nestefus Nucallodem<br>Lvl 55 Evoker<br>House of Elder - Tarrew Marr<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br><br><br></td></tr>
